Package com.googlecode.janrain4j.api.engage.response.poco

Provides Engage API response classes related to portable contacts.

          Description

Class Summary
Account Online account held by the Contact.
Address Physical mailing address for the Contact.
Contact A dictionary containing the Portable Contacts data.
Email Email address for the Contact.
IM Instant messaging address for the Contact.
Name Name of the Contact.
Organization Current or past organizational affiliation of the Contact.
PhoneNumber Phone number for the Contact.
Photo URL of a photo of the Contact.
Relationship Bi-directionally asserted relationship type that was established between the user and the Contact by the Service Provider.
Url URL of a web page related to the Contact.
